</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Z motion system Height Adjustment right motor</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 03M3 </compcodenr><compsignal class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal " translate="no">ZMS_HA_RIGHT_MO</compsignal></comp>. 
